snippet: “People are fed up” with the debate over whether Quebec should separate from Canada, one commentator wrote.
abstract: Crushing defeat of Quebec separatist group Parti Quebecois in recent election means that no party with any aspiration of holding power will openly promote referendum on separating from Canada for years to come.
lead_paragraph: “People are fed up” with the debate over whether Quebec should separate from Canada, one commentator wrote.

headline.main: Parti Québécois Failed to Renew Mandate, Analysts Say
headline.print_headline: Parti Québécois Failed to Renew Mandate, Analysts Say
